ModzTeam Modern Ops arm64 Menu 
-----------------------------------

This package contains a mod menu for Modern Ops, includes a total of 9 features. To request an update ask me in the comment section of the YouTube video.

This package will be frequently updated with more features as I find them.

Disclaimer
----
I take no responsibility of anything that you do with this mod, remember that cheating eventually results in a ban. That is not our fault nor problem. Enjoy! 

#### Do not share deb to anyone, share the repo instead. This makes it easier to push updates for everyone. Thank you.

Features
----

- Custom Speed

- Chams

- Red Crosshair

- Unlock Guns

- No Spread

- Custom XP

- Custom Levels

- Custom Trophies

- Custom Season Pass XP

#### Version 1.1

	
• Split arm64 and arm64e support to prevent crashes on some devices
